	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=154388><span id= >HeroFromHyrule</span></a><br><span id=notbold>5 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>When Adida said the he/she gets more health with the spell, it was because of AA.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can get AA abilities to increase your HP regeneration, so, if your natural HP regeneration is more than 4 hp per tick, then you will lose 4hp a tick and gain 8 mana, but also regen some hp at the same time.  So, if you regen 6 hp a tick, 4 of it turns into 8 mana, every tick you would gain 2 hp and 8 mana (not counting meditation skill).  Pretty handy, but only works if you have AA skills (or if you have Regen cast on you).<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Sep 20 17:15:54 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
